<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,355,1646,1672]" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">Distribution:</emphasis>
Western part of the Aleutian Islands, Kiska-Harbor Bay, Commander Island, at depths between 
<quantity box="[151,250,1683,1709]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.9" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="1.8" pageId="41" pageNumber="42" unit="m" value="29.0" valueMax="40.0" valueMin="18.0">18–40 m</quantity>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Kussakin, O. G." box="[264,438,1683,1709]" pageId="41" pageNumber="42" pagination="1 - 463" refId="ref19608" refString="Kussakin, O. G. (1982) Morskye I solonovatovodnye ravnonogie rakoobrasnye (Isopoda) cholodnix I umerennix vod severnogo polushariya [Marine and brackish water like-footed crustaceans (Isopoda) of cold and temperate waters of the North- ern Hemisphere]. Podotryadi Anthuridea, Microcerberidea, Valvifera, Tyloidea. Opredeliteli po Faune SSSR, Izdavaemye Zoologicheskim Institutom Akademii Nauk SSSR, 131 (2), 1 - 463. [in Russian]" type="journal article" year="1982">Kussakin 1982</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
